cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.CR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with automated monitoring of construction sites using images and videos from surveillance cameras. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes the use of deep neural networks for asset monitoring. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses the use of clustering algorithms to improve the performance of the Single-Shot Multibox Detector. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper deals with automation of monitoring tasks. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category as it is not directly related to the content of the paper.
